
## Identity Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    User[User Device] --> Login[User Login]
    Login --> EntraID[Microsoft Entra ID]

    EntraID --> MFA[Multi-Factor Authentication]
    MFA --> CA[Conditional Access Policies]

    CA --> Exchange[Exchange Online]
    CA --> Teams[Microsoft Teams]
    CA --> SharePoint[SharePoint Online]
    CA --> OneDrive[OneDrive]
```
